    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/flex-lenders-reborrow">
                                    “You’re Already Approved”: How One Tennessee Company Sets a Debt Trap
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Borrowers say the lending company Advance Financial encouraged them to borrow back the value of almost all of the payments they made, tearing a hole in the safety net the law tried to create.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
                        <span class="story-card__byline-author">
                by <span class="name">Adam Friedman</span>, <a href="https://tennesseelookout.com/">Tennessee Lookout</a>,
            </span>
                        <span class="story-card__byline-dateline">
                <time class="timestamp" datetime="2025-06-26EDT05:00">June 26, 2025, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
            </span>
        </p>

                <p class="story-card__unit">Local Reporting Network</p>
            </div>
</div>
    

        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    

                    
                    
    
        <div class="lead-art">
            <a class="aspect-3-2" href="https://www.propublica.org/article/charles-carrier-plea-deal-fraud">
                <img
